{"id":1034,"date":"2026-03-19T15:38:13","date_gmt":"2026-03-19T10:08:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/?p=1034"},"modified":"2026-03-19T15:46:00","modified_gmt":"2026-03-19T10:16:00","slug":"web-development-competition-on-20-03-2026","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/web-development-competition-on-20-03-2026\/","title":{"rendered":"Web Development Competition on 20.03.2026"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-aa74a584-f20a-4d59-9960-ee14d7d2b94c\" href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Web-Development-Competition.jpeg\">Web Development Competition<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/Web-Development-Competition.jpeg\" class=\"wp-block-file__button wp-element-button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-aa74a584-f20a-4d59-9960-ee14d7d2b94c\">Download<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><br>Competition Guidelines<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Participants must carry their own laptops for the event.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Limited internet usage will be permitted during the competition.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Students can participate individually or as part of a team.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Participants must develop a fully functional website\/web app based on the given theme.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Final submissions must include:<br>Complete source code.<br>Project documentation, details.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Original Work Only:<br>Plagiarism is strictly prohibited.<br>Pre-built or previously developed projects will not be accepted.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Coding must begin only after the official start of the competition.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>All participants must adhere to the rules and guidance provided by the coordinators.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>You are free to use any technology stack of your choice.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Preferred stacks: MERN, MEAN, PERN, T3 Stack.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Marking Scheme (100 Marks)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\udca1 Idea &amp; Innovation \u2013 15<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83c\udfaf Relevance to Theme \u2013 10<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83e\udde0 Approach &amp; Problem Solving \u2013 15<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\udcbb Functionality &amp; Performance \u2013 20<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83c\udfa8 UI\/UX Design \u2013 15<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83e\udde9 Code Quality \u2013 15<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\ud83d\udc69\ud83c\udffb\u200d\ud83c\udfeb Presentation \u2013 10<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Competition Guidelines Marking Scheme (100 Marks) \ud83d\udca1 Idea &amp; Innovation \u2013 15 \ud83c\udfaf Relevance to Theme \u2013 10 \ud83e\udde0 Approach &amp; Problem Solving \u2013 15 \ud83d\udcbb Functionality &amp; Performance \u2013 20 \ud83c\udfa8 UI\/UX Design \u2013 15 \ud83e\udde9 Code Quality \u2013 15 \ud83d\udc69\ud83c\udffb\u200d\ud83c\udfeb Presentation \u2013 10<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_kad_post_transparent":"","_kad_post_title":"","_kad_post_layout":"","_kad_post_sidebar_id":"","_kad_post_content_style":"","_kad_post_vertical_padding":"","_kad_post_feature":"","_kad_post_feature_position":"","_kad_post_header":false,"_kad_post_footer":false,"_kad_post_classname":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1034","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-updates"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1034","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sietpanchkula.ac.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1034"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https: